  "prompt": "Can we swallow fenugreek seeds as a whole?",
  "response": "Yes, you can swallow fenugreek seeds whole, but there are a few things to consider. Whole seeds may not be as easily digested as crushed or soaked seeds, which can help release their nutrients. Many people find that soaking the seeds overnight or grinding them before consumption improves digestibility and taste. Additionally, if you're considering fenugreek seeds for health benefits, crushed or soaked seeds may offer more advantages. Always consult with a healthcare professional if you have specific health concerns or conditions.",
